---
import MelvinLayout from '../../../layouts/MelvinLayout.astro';
---

<MelvinLayout 
    title="Vision 2030"
    description="Melvin Lim's 10-year roadmap. From mastering First Principles of Law to advocating for Restorative Justice and Public Policy."
>
    <section class="page-header container">
        <span class="eyebrow">The Road Ahead</span>
        <h1>Vision 2030</h1>
        <p class="lead">From the parade square to the courtroom. My plan for the next decade.</p>
        <div class="hypothesis-badge">
            <span class="badge-icon">⚠️</span> 
            <span class="badge-text"><strong>Current Hypothesis:</strong> This roadmap is a living document. Subject to evolution, failure, and new data.</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="vision-grid container">
        
        <!-- Pillar 1: Academic -->
        <article class="vision-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-header">
                <span class="step-number">01</span>
                <h2>Legal Scholarship</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-content">
                <p class="objective"><strong>Objective:</strong> To master the first principles of Law and Political Economy.</p>
                <ul class="roadmap-list">
                    <li><strong>Targets:</strong> NUS or SMU Law (Class of 2027)</li>
                    <li><strong>Specialization:</strong> Public, Administrative, and Criminal Law</li>
                    <li><strong>Research Focus:</strong> <em>Restorative Justice Frameworks in Urban Societies</em></li>
                    <li><strong>Aspiration:</strong> Balancing deterrent frameworks with empathetic rehabilitation.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Pillar 2: Professional -->
        <article class="vision-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-header">
                <span class="step-number">02</span>
                <h2>Litigation & Advocacy</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-content">
                <p class="objective"><strong>Objective:</strong> To practice law with technical excellence and moral clarity.</p>
                <ul class="roadmap-list">
                    <li>Training Contract at a Big 4 Firm (Dispute Resolution)</li>
                    <li>Pro Bono Practice: Criminal Legal Aid Scheme (CLAS)</li>
                    <li>Focus: Commercial Litigation & White Collar Crime</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Pillar 3: Impact -->
        <article class="vision-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-header">
                <span class="step-number">03</span>
                <h2>Public Policy</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-content">
                <p class="objective"><strong>Objective:</strong> To shape the systems that shape us.</p>
                <p class="narrative">
                    Law is the operating system of society. My long-term ambition is to segue from practice into policy formulation, ensuring that our legal frameworks remain robust yet humane in an increasingly complex world.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

    </section>

    <section class="quote-interlude container">
        <blockquote>"Law is order, and good law is good order."</blockquote>
        <cite>— Aristotle</cite>
    </section>

</MelvinLayout>

<style>
    .page-header {
        padding-top: 8rem;
        padding-bottom: 4rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .eyebrow {
        font-family: var(--mv-font-sans);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        color: var(--mv-accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .lead {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--mv-text-muted);
        max-width: 600px;
    }

    .vision-grid {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .vision-pillar {
        padding-right: 2rem;
    }

    .pillar-header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .step-number {
        font-family: var(--mv-font-mono);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        display: block;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .vision-pillar h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .pillar-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--mv-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pillar-content strong {
        color: var(--mv-text-main);
    }

    .roadmap-list li strong {
        color: var(--mv-text-main);
    }

    /* Hypothesis Badge (Red Team Fix) */
    .hypothesis-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
        background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05); /* Gold tint */
        border: 1px dashed rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-family: var(--mv-font-mono);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--mv-text-muted);
        max-width: 500px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .badge-icon {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .roadmap-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .roadmap-list li {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--mv-text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .roadmap-list li::before {
        content: '→';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--mv-accent);
    }

    .quote-interlude {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 0 8rem 0;
    }

    .quote-interlude blockquote {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-family: var(--mv-font-serif);
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--mv-text-main);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .vision-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
        
        .vision-pillar {
            padding-right: 0;
        }
    }
</style>
